<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .header { background: #4A5D4F; color: white; padding: 24px; text-align: center; }
    .header h2 { margin: 0; }
    .body { padding: 24px; }
    .detail-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; font-size: 14px; }
    .detail-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .card { border: 1px solid #dee2e6; border-radius: 6px; padding: 16px; margin: 16px 0; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background: #4A5D4F; color: white; padding: 14px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 16px; }
    .note { background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 6px; padding: 12px 16px; font-size: 13px; color: #6c757d; margin-top: 16px; }
    .stars { color: #ffc107; font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: 2px; }
    .footer { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 16px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #6c757d; margin-top: 24px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h2>How was your appointment?</h2>
    <p style="margin:8px 0 0; opacity:0.9;">We'd love to hear about your experience</p>
  </div>
  <div class="body">
    <p>Hi <%= @customer.name %>,</p>

    <p>Your appointment with <strong><%= @stylist.name %></strong> has been marked as complete. We hope it was a great experience!</p>

    <div class="stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="detail-row"><span>Stylist</span><strong><%= @stylist.name %></strong></div>
      <% if @appointment.selected_service.present? %>
        <div class="detail-row"><span>Service</span><strong><%= @appointment.selected_service.split(' - $').first %></strong></div>
      <% end %>
      <div class="detail-row"><span>Date</span><strong><%= @appointment.time.strftime("%A, %B %-d, %Y") %></strong></div>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 24px 0;">
      <a href="<%= new_appointment_review_url(@appointment) %>" class="btn">Leave a Review</a>
    </div>

    <div class="note">
      <strong>Note:</strong> You have <strong>3 days</strong> from your appointment completion to leave a review. After that, the review window will close.
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">&copy; ChairHop &middot; You're receiving this because you completed an appointment on ChairHop.</div>
</body>
</html>
